PLA_CMN_20070103.0175	0	30010.000	30019.900				Why would Ningbo Fubang jointly establish a club with the Bayi Men's Basketball Team?	0	0	0		
PLA_CMN_20070103.0175	0	30020.000	30029.900				The Chairman of the Fubang Group, Song Hanping, believed that the establishment of Bayi Fubang Men's Professional Basketball Club meets the needs in constructing a harmonious society and building a civilized city spirit, which was an important measure in promoting military and civilian unity, military and civilian friendship, and was the warm expectation of the general Ningbo basketball fans.	0	0	0		
PLA_CMN_20070103.0175	0	40010.000	40019.900				On many occasions, Song Hanping has revealed this kind of spirit: Setting up a club is not negotiating businesses or doing transactions. Through the club operation, we want to organically unite the team spirit, and the fighting spirit in the Bayi Men's Basketball Teams in striving for success with Fubang Group's enterprising spirit of adventurous exploration and future transcendence, to make a bigger contribution to Ningbo's economic development and spiritual civilization construction.	0	0	0		
PLA_CMN_20070103.0175	0	40020.000	40029.900				Why would Bayi Men's Basketball Team set up a club?	0	0	0		
