PLA_CMN_20070103.0175	0	40040.000	40049.900				In other words, it is to develop and enhance the level of our military basketball sports, make a bigger contribution to our country's basketball enterprise, promote military and civil administration, military and civilian unity, and make a bigger and new contribution to promoting a harmonious society.	0	0	0		
